t be said that God created the Sabbath, for </div><div class="t m321 xb9 h28 y1535 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">as portions of the earth&apos;s substance had been fashioned by the Creator into </div><div class="t m1839 x3 h28 y12e2 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">plants, animals, and humanity, and were by Him infused with life; and as </div><div class="t m812 x97 h2b y8a2 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[ 3 ] </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
